Command-notification, a Pidgin plugin
----------------

Command-notification is a small rewrite of the plugin by Simo Mattila called led-notification
It will let you exacute a given command when a new message is received and a
second command when all notifications are gone.

Simo Mattila <simo.h.mattila@gmail.com>
http://koti.mbnet.fi/simom/

